ookup, and instantiation.\n- Added `tests/src/org.mockito/mockito-core/5.0.0/src/test/resources/mockito-extensions/org.mockito.plugins.MockResolver`\n  - Points Mockito’s public plugin discovery to the test resolver.\n- Updated `tests/src/org.mockito/mockito-core/5.0.0/user-code-filter.json`\n  - Includes the resolver class narrowly so Native Image metadata generation can retain its reflective constructor access.\n\nI did not run/compile tests, per instruction. Note: `dynamic-access-exhaust-report.json` was already modified in the worktree before my changes.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_048174b4aab1d6f7016a2aba381ba08194987f60e13b799daa\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 389, "output": 718, "cacheRead": 35840, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 36947, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781185065417, "responseId": "resp_048174b4aab1d6f7016a2aba2a1cbc81949641d3836a55bb28"}, "toolResults": []}
